title: Police arrest Ex-Prince Andrew. And, Trump hosts the first Board of Peace meeting
description: U.K. police arrested Former Prince Andrew today on suspicion of misconduct in public office, U.K. media reports. And, President Trump is hosting the first-ever Board of Peace meeting today.
